    {
      "text": "Gotouchi Hello Kitty Sugoroku Monogatari is a game developed by Sanrio Digital and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2003.\nThe game features 2d cartoon graphics & up to 4 human players or play against 1 or 3 computer players.",
      "lang": "en",
